Environment variable settings for MAS

The following environment variables should be set to run the market analysis
server (shown with example settings):

MAS_MAILER=elm
MAS_DIRECTORY=~/.mas
MAS_STOCK_SPLIT_FILE=stock_splits
MAS_MAILER_SUBJECT_FLAG=-s

MAS_MAILER specifies the email client that will be used by MAS.
MAS_MAILER_SUBJECT_FLAG specifies the command-line flag used by the mailer
to specify that the next argument is the email message subject.
MAS_DIRECTORY specifies the directory MAS will look in for configuration
information, such as user-defined indicators.
MAS_STOCK_SPLIT_FILE specifies the name of a file containing stock split
information.
